				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hbox {Fe}_{\text {4}}$$\end{document}-based SMMs could be successfully grafted on CNTs [106]. Moreover, proteins can be bound on the CNT [107]. Furthermore, van der Waals interactions also proved to be suited, which has been shown for nanoparticles [108]. Encapsulation of Mn12\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
